info.description:
Humble: GitHub User Stats
=========================



Features:
---------

- Lists a user's repos.


Installation
------------

To install humble, simply: ::

    $ pip install humble

Or, if you absolutely must: ::

    $ easy_install humble

But, you really shouldn't do that.
